{"text_id":217007,"tokens":["If"," you"," are"," a"," small"," investor"," with"," a"," low"," net"," worth"," and"," you"," are"," facing"," a"," bearish"," market",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," remember"," to"," keep"," a"," long","-","term"," perspective"," and"," not"," to"," panic","."," Here"," are"," a"," few"," tips"," for"," professional"," investment"," planning"," in"," a"," bearish"," market",":","Diver","sify"," your"," portfolio",":"," Don","'","t"," put"," all"," your"," eggs"," in"," one"," basket","."," Spread"," your"," investments"," across"," a"," variety"," of"," asset"," classes",","," such"," as"," stocks",","," bonds",","," and"," cash","."," This"," will"," help"," to"," mitigate"," the"," impact"," of"," a"," bear"," market"," on"," your"," portfolio",".","Consider"," dollar","-","cost"," averaging",":"," This"," is"," a"," strategy"," where"," you"," invest"," a"," fixed"," amount"," of"," money"," at"," regular"," intervals",","," regardless"," of"," the"," price"," of"," the"," investment","."," This"," can"," help"," to"," smooth"," out"," the"," impact"," of"," market"," fluctuations"," on"," your"," portfolio",".","Think"," about"," your"," risk"," tolerance",":"," Make"," sure"," that"," your"," investments"," are"," appropriate"," for"," your"," risk"," tolerance","."," If"," you"," are"," more"," risk","-","a","verse",","," you"," may"," want"," to"," allocate"," a"," larger"," portion"," of"," your"," portfolio"," to"," safer"," investments"," like"," bonds",".","Keep"," a"," long","-","term"," perspective",":"," Bear"," markets"," are"," generally"," temporary"," and"," the"," stock"," market"," has"," historically"," trend","ed"," upwards"," over"," the"," long"," run","."," Try"," to"," stay"," focused"," on"," your"," long","-","term"," financial"," goals"," and"," resist"," the"," temptation"," to"," sell"," off"," your"," investments"," in"," a"," panic",".","Consider"," working"," with"," a"," financial"," advisor","